div.div:
Get answer from RabbitMQ queue
1. Connect to remoteÂ queue with <queue_name> param (from `New queue-register url` action)
2. Get from queue last message, check <id>(forÂ RuCaptcha) and <taskId>(forÂ AntiCaptcha), and if all is ok makeÂ "Delivery processing acknowledgementsÂ from consumer to publisher".
3. Use <code>(for RuCaptcha) and<message>(for AntiCaptcha) from message to solve captcha.

div.div:
Get answer from cache
1. Send GET requests to server.Â
Â Â Set params:
Â Â Â Â http://85.255.8.26:8001/<service_name>/cache/<task_id>
2. Get response in JSON format, like:
Â Â If RuCaptcha send response to our server:
Â Â Â {'id': <task_id>, 'code': <solve_code>}
Â Â or if captcha still not ready:
Â Â Â {'id': <task_id>, 'code': "CAPCHA_NOT_READY"}
Â Â
Â Â If AntiCaptcha send response to our server:
Â Â Â {'taskId': <task_id>, 'message': {......}}
Â Â or if captcha still not ready:
Â Â Â {'taskId': <task_id>, 'message': {'taskId': <task_id>, 'status': 'processing'}}

div.h1: Plan for RuCaptcha service and callback
div.p: 1. Register new queue on callback server.
2. Create new captcha-solve task with `pingback` param.
3. You have two variants to get captcha solving data:

Â Â 3.1 Connect to RabbitMQ queue and wait message. Using this URL to login, and waiting message:Â
Â Â Â Â Â Â Â amqp://hardworker_1:password@85.255.8.26:5672/rucaptcha_vhost;
Â Â 3.2 Send GET requests to our server (and get data from cache);
4. Solve your captcha using <code> from response.

div.h1: Plan for AntiCaptcha service and callback
div.p: 1. Register new queue on callback server.
2. Create new captcha-solve task with `callbackUrl` param.
3. You have two variants to get captcha solving data:

Â Â 3.1 Connect to RabbitMQ queue and wait message. Using this URL to login, and waiting message:Â
Â Â Â Â Â Â Â amqp://hardworker_1:password@85.255.8.26:5672/anticaptcha_vhost;
Â Â 3.2 Send GET requests to our server (and get data from cache);
4. Solve your captcha using <solution> from response (responseÂ similar to the contents of getTaskResult method).
